Package apoc.couchbase.document

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CouchbaseDocument<T>
    This interface redefines the Couchbase Document interface just by slightly changing it with valid data types for neo4j procedures.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CouchbaseJsonDocument
    Represents a Document that contains a JSON object as the content.
    CouchbaseQueryResult
    Transports the list of JsonObjects retrieved by a N1QL query so that it can be Stream-ed and returned by the procedures

    Every JsonObjects retrieved by a N1QL query is first converted into a Map<String, Object> and then added to the embedded CouchbaseQueryResult.queryResult list.
    CouchbaseUtils
    Utility class for Couchbase procedures.
